 rituals with ease and peace of mind.The guide serves as an interactive educational resource covering all stages of the Umrah and visit journey, from pre-travel preparations and visa and permit procedures to performing the rituals, facilitating movement at the Two Holy Mosques, and completing departure formalities.The guide presents information chronologically, allowing Umrah performers and visitors quick access to content relevant to each stage of their journey. It includes visual elements and digital links to maps, instructional videos, and support services. It features instructions for Ihram, Tawaf, Sa'i, and the etiquette of the Two Holy Mosques. The guide also highlights essential services at the Grand Mosque in Makkah and the Prophet's Mosque in Madinah, along with organizational and behavioral guidelines to maintain order and facilitate smooth movement.The ministry emphasized that the issuance of the Umrah and Visit Guide is part of its ongoing efforts to enhance the experience of worshipers and Umrah pilgrims, raise procedural and organizational awareness, and support digital transformation in services. The guide aims to facilitate the journey of Umrah pilgrims and visitors and to improve service quality, and is available online at www.haj.gov.sa/Guides.", "content": "ONLY AVAILABLE IN PAID PLANS", "keywords": ["\u0622\u062e\u0631 \u0627\u0644\u0627\u062e\u0628\u0627\u0631"], "creator": ["saudi gazette report"], "language": "english", "country": ["saudi arabia"], "category": ["lifestyle", "top"], "datatype": "news", "pubDate": "2026-02-22 21:02:42", "pubDateTZ": "UTC", "fetched_at": "2026-02-22 21:43:51", "image_url": "https://saudigazette.com.sa/saudigazette/uploads/images/2026/02/23/2667488.webp", "video_url": null, "source_id": "saudigazette", "source_name": "Saudi Gazette", "source_priority": 356263, "source_url": "https://saudigazette.com.sa", "source_icon": "https://n.bytvi.com/saudigazette.png", "sentiment": "ONLY AVAILABLE IN PROFESSIONAL AND CORPORA